 awareness among the rural populations. Thanks to what I learned about ROAM, we have a technique that will lead to action plans and decisions on the most appropriate activities for each province and ethnic group.\u201d In addition to mustering popular support for landscape restoration,", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "f54708c0-a0b4-42da-ac0a-614e8736dd2e": {"__data__": {"id_": "f54708c0-a0b4-42da-ac0a-614e8736dd2e", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/leaders-action-achieving-forest-landscape-restoration-through-online", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Leaders in action : achieving forest landscape restoration through online learning", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/leaders-action-achieving-forest-landscape-restoration-through-online", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "abf9d8b818b8c04c26a1b360de57387c92a99aa1b532c41d4d96af0eb84637a1"}, "3": {"node_id": "9a870d46-18d0-4ade-9c8e-5bdbbdda26c6", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/leaders-action-achieving-forest-landscape-restoration-through-online", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "5fe15896c9c4009d94c6bc4c59ded112d450290dfba5afb42e4f65d27f81eb86"}}, "hash": "d883a39cd683201ba86d98cdce17dc47917284683b0c4641978fe7e627355537", "text": "he and his department ar